ygData.messageBody:
I know this is an older message but I'm just now getting to my email.
You can get maps from http://maps.eq-toolbox.com
you download them into your Maps folder unde your EverQuest directory.
When you view the maps make sure you have the option ... I'm not remembering exactly what it's called.. but ther'es an option to only show things on the same elevation as you... Make sure that is off.
Hope this helps.
I'm going to go to sleep now..
luv,
-Su
